---
import PageLayout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { getPermalink } from '~/utils/permalinks';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Services',
  description:
    'Interior styling and consultation services by Thyra Löwenmark. Clear deliverables, practical guidance, and a cohesive plan for your home.',
};
---

<PageLayout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14 md:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold md:text-5xl">Services</h1>
    <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg opacity-90">
      Thyra’s services are designed to remove uncertainty and help you make confident decisions—whether you need quick direction
      or a structured plan. Sessions are available remotely, and in-person by arrangement.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Mini Consult (60 min)</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm opacity-90">
          Fast clarity for one space or one design problem. Ideal when you feel stuck and need professional direction.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm opacity-90">
          <li>Layout and flow recommendations</li>
          <li>Palette direction (color + materials)</li>
          <li>Lighting suggestions for warmth and function</li>
          <li>Prioritized next steps</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm opacity-75">Price: From SEK X</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Room Plan</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm opacity-90">
          A structured plan for one room, with a cohesive direction and practical guidance to execute.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm opacity-90">
          <li>Concept direction (palette, materials, mood)</li>
          <li>Shopping list with key product categories</li>
          <li>Styling guidance (art, textiles, accessories)</li>
          <li>Phasing suggestions if you want to do it over time</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm opacity-75">Price: From SEK X</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Styling Session</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm opacity-90">
          Hands-on support to make your space feel finished—best for final adjustments and photo-ready polish.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm opacity-90">
          <li>Placement and styling of what you already own</li>
          <li>Textiles, art, and finishing touches</li>
          <li>Optional add-on: curated purchases</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm opacity-75">Price: From SEK X</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">How it works</h3>
        <ol class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-sm opacity-90">
          <li><strong>1) Intake:</strong> photos, goals, inspiration, and budget range.</li>
          <li><strong>2) Session:</strong> define priorities and direction.</li>
          <li><strong>3) Deliverables:</strong> a plan with clear next steps and curated options.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What you’ll get</h3>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm opacity-90">
          <li><strong>Clarity:</strong> a prioritized action plan.</li>
          <li><strong>Cohesion:</strong> a palette and styling direction that flows.</li>
          <li><strong>Practicality:</strong> decisions that match function, budget, and timeline.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 rounded-3xl border p-8 md:p-10">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Not sure where to start?</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-sm opacity-90">
        Send a few photos and a short description of what you want to improve. Thyra will recommend the best service.
      </p>
      <a class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-2xl bg-black px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white hover:opacity-90" href={getPermalink('contact')}>
        Contact Thyra
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
